{"type": "article", "id": 21980, "title": "巧克力包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-05T08:00:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 75, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702164707FSUaGr5ZjRcxyMY7.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是日本平面设计师 Yuta Takahashi 带来的巧克力包装，他将包装设计成信件的样式。正反两面是纯白色的，只有非常少的黑色印刷体文字，清晰而诗意。Mandarin Natural Chocolate 宣称只使用有机可可和蔗糖，极简的包装也表现出天然和纯粹。一些隐藏信息蕴含其中，比如下面一排黑点有 10 个，代表了可可的浓度。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164704VfqUWxTmN9ACct3M.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164704TnJrkyLWzMdxfvbF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80235043\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164705iBNg0AcRw3YFPDqo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021647054Vc0RwJMIzaSrCve.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71367521\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021647061hqSOxwKCYF3EQbJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99893162\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}